title: Do they make up for two examples of the universe, such as two doses of Prozac's proselytism?
subtitle: There is no evidence that two "clans" of cashews are as effective as a dose of prozac, although Mimi says otherwise.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: A few cashews are equivalent to one dose of prozac in the treatment of depression, and can safely be replaced with prescribed drugs.
